name: CEMENT MASCOT
description:
Take your team to the streets and go get it this fall. Need a mascot? We got your back...

Whether it's the AJ III's for the casual cement print look or a nice pair of AJ VII's for the serious grind...Blacksheep always comes with you.
 
Stand Out every damn day.   


Printed on 4.5-ounce, 100% pre-shrunk cotton.
